WEBVTT

00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:31.456
And there are four goals
that need to be fulfilled in your goal

00:05:31.480 --> 00:05:32.920
in order for this to work.

00:05:34.440 --> 00:05:38.776
These four criteria
are that your goal must be:

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:43.800
tangible, credible, inclusive and epic.

00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:47.600
Let's take a look at them:
It needs to be tangible.

00:05:48.200 --> 00:05:49.416
A lot of people say,

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:52.176
"Well, you know, we should make
the world a better place,"

00:05:52.200 --> 00:05:55.560
or, "Yeah, we should all feel good now."

00:05:57.360 --> 00:05:58.560
Not going to work.

00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:01.000
You need a binary.